dmca.principal_name: NetSila SAL, the owner of shahiya.com. I am Director at NetSila SAL

works.description:
The whole recipe "فيتوشيني ألفريدو دايت" is copied from shahiya.com. It was written by Carole Makhoul Hani, partner at shahiya.com.

Can we talk to someone directly? Our original - moderated recipes - have been copied hundreds if not thousands of times. Very often, the copies appear higher in google search results than our original content!
